title: POS_001
extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was isolated from NP swabs in viral transport media using the Roche MagNAPure or Qiagen BioRobot
extract_protocol_ch1.1: First strand cDNA was synthesized by SuperScriptIV/Random hexamers, second strand by Sequenase v2.0, and libraries constructed by Nextera XT Kit
data_processing: Illumina Casava1.7 software used for basecalling.
data_processing.1: Single end reads were adapter and quality trimmed by Trimmomatic v0.39, aligned to Ensembl v96 human transcriptome by Kallisto v0.46, and collapsed to gene level annotations by Biomart. Only samples with >500000 human reads were included for further analysis
data_processing.2: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: Matrix table with raw gene counts for every gene and every sample
